{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/TripKitAPI\/documentation\/TripKitAPI\/TKAPI\/Vehicle\/components"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"TripKitAPI"}],"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"components","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": [[","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10TripKitAPI5TKAPIV17VehicleComponentsV","text":"VehicleComponents","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"]]?","kind":"text"}],"title":"components","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10TripKitAPI5TKAPIV7VehicleV10componentsSaySayAC0E10ComponentsVGGSgvp"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/TripKitAPI\/documentation\/TripKitAPI","doc:\/\/TripKitAPI\/documentation\/TripKitAPI\/TKAPI","doc:\/\/TripKitAPI\/documentation\/TripKitAPI\/TKAPI\/Vehicle"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Components of this vehicle with additional information."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"components"},{"kind":"text","text":": [["},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/TripKitAPI\/documentation\/TripKitAPI\/TKAPI\/VehicleComponents","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"VehicleComponents","preciseIdentifier":"s:10TripKitAPI5TKAPIV17VehicleComponentsV"},{"kind":"text","text":"]]?"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The top level array represents connected parts of the vehicle, which you can’t walk through"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"without leaving the vehicle (e.g., two trains connected together). The inner level array"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"represents then parts that can be walked through (e.g., the carriages of a train). A bus"},{"type":"text","t